Nimbula,has,developed,an,automated,cloud,management,system,delivering,Amazon,EC,like,services,behind,the,firewall,Their,Nimbula,Cloud,OS,also,comes,with,an,API,to,manage,on,and,off,site,cloud,computing,resources,The,Nimbula,API,is,a,RESTful,HTTP,API,with,JSON,encoding,supports,a,rich,set,of,functionality,and,a,simple,and,robust,interface,to,cloud,resources